supportingHeading: Web designers and developers are often looked at as the enemy, but the truth is that they are just trying to make a living. They have bills to pay like everyone else. I am a web designer myself and it's not an easy job.
secondaryContent: I am sick of seeing people getting extorted by web designers who charge way too much for their services. So I've made webgu - an AI-powered website builder that will let you build your own website without any coding knowledge required. It's free, easy to use, and you don't need any design skills to build a beautiful website with it!
